(214, '2021-08-22 10:21:39', 'Leon G', 'mapple.lai@gmail.com', 'For engineering course, UNIMAS provides each faculty for each department, as well as sufficient laboratory equipment that suits the syllabus. For environment, there is a lake at the centre of UNIMAS, where students can kayak or chilling beside the lake. Other than that, the campus is clean and convenient for students who walk and cycle. For lecture, most of the lecturers done their master and PhD qualification, and therefore provides excellent teaching methods. For food, there are a variety of cafes nearby the faculties and college (place to stay). But the food are mostly Fried noddles, rice or self-taken mix vegetables, roti canai but it is rare to see chinese cusine. For management, there are many clubs that handles student affairs and settle studentâ€™s problems if they are any. Overall, I think UNIMAS is consider good.', 'Civil Engineering', 2018, 30, 4, 5, 4, 3, 4, 1, NULL),
(215, '2021-08-22 11:47:06', 'Tui Ai Qin', 'tuiaq-wk19@student.tarc.edu.my', 'Not much to comment since e-learning from year 1 sem 3. The lecture are just good keep tracking with us and update us with recent trend and discuss the future possibilities of our industry. Therefore our syllabus has became more real life industry based because our syllabus was consulted with real time industry so that we can catch up in terms of technical, and management skills. ', 'Broadcasting', 2020, 78, 3, 4, 4, 5, 2, 1, NULL),
(216, '2021-08-22 12:16:07', 'Angelrene Goh', 'angelrene1128@gmail.com', 'Lecturers in my course are very helpful, friendly, and  kind. They give clear lectures and ready to help us. They will repeat everything again if you are lost and you asked question. Some lecturers even want us to ask questions everytime before the class ends to ensure we fully understood what we have learnt.\r\n\r\nNevertheless, some improvements may be needed for this university. \r\nFrankly speaking, I believe every university has its own problem. Just one thing I would suggest to the UCSI management. Maybe we can avoid last minute announcement, be a little bit more concerning about the students, in terms of their financial condition, and then both of us can achieve a win-win situation. \r\n\r\nThanks for reading till here. Have a nice day ahead!! :)', 'Bachelor of Pharmacy', 2021, 46, 3, 3, 4, 3, 1, 1, NULL),
(217, '2021-08-22 13:21:17', 'Alan ', 'alan-98@live.com.my', 'UNIMAS has a wide variety of fully functioning laboratory equipments for civil engineering related course, from 8 meters hydraulic flume to machinery for soil triaxial test, its availability of equipments and experienced lab technicians allow students to gain substantial knowledge on essential investigative testing in civil engineering field. \r\n\r\nApart from that, majority of the lecturers are professional who has experiences on actual civil engineering works, students\' questions rarely goes unanswered, more often than not they provide more details on real life application of the knowledge based on their knowledge than we anticipated. \r\n\r\nGeneral facilities are widely available such as parking space, food kiosk with seats & tables, coin laundry, cafe and so on. Academic facilities such as lecture halls, tutorial rooms, library etc are also available in large quantities to cater for academic needs. However, some of the facilities can be improved in terms of maintenance works to make sure everything is in working order.\r\n\r\nFood are widely available in the campus. With many stores available at Student Pavillion/Lakeview cafe, there seems to be many choices of food for student. However, the food choice are limited to Malay cuisine and western cuisine. With fried food dominating the market, it can be difficult to seek for less oily food sometimes, especially during evening time.\r\n\r\nIn terms of environment, UNIMAS is a beautiful university. It has a beautiful manmade lake that is ideal for recreational activities. It is common to see kayak club actively kayaking on the lake. It also serve as a good place for exercise such as jogging. Due to somewhat low traffic in the campus, the air is usually very clean and refreshing, especially in the early morning and late evening.', 'Civil Engineering', 2018, 30, 3, 5, 5, 2, 5, 1, NULL),
