(237, '2021-08-23 12:26:45', 'Lai Wai Kuan', 'kuanjuseyo1826@gmail.com', 'Nice memories in campus during diploma time because I have the chance to study at the campus for 2 years and I am sure it is better than e-learning. :) Some lecturers are very experience, friendly and treat you like their friends and even handle the e-learning very well. However, ofc there are \"not so good\" lecturers. TARUC facilities is not like perfect but quite nice too. There is just one thing I very curious about, why is TARUC mostly Chinese students? HAHAHA I really wanna make friends with different races. Food is ok. å†¬è‡è‚‰é†¬æ‹‰éºµ the best HAHAHA.', 'Broadcasting', 2018, 78, 4, 4, 4, 3, 3, 1, NULL),
