(247, '2021-08-25 13:37:56', 'YeeCK', 'keryc-wk18@student.tarc.edu.my', 'Overall is good. Under the e-learning due to COVID-19, the solutions or amendments made to the course syllabus are acceptable, however, the management or lecturer should be more concern about students\' safety under current situation as some students have to complete their coursework outdoor like shooting although the covid cases reached 20k+. Hence, the communication between students and the lecturer/management should be more efficient. But,before that, campus did help those students in need with food supplies and latest information provided as week which is very useful and helpful. ', 'Broadcasting', 2021, 78, 4, 5, 4, 4, 4, 1, NULL),
