(260, '2021-08-26 17:05:16', 'UCHIHA ITACH', 'Semleel2367@gmail.com', '\r\n1. VERY UNSATISFIED with the timetable arrangement. Saturday class too much and left other days have only 1 or 2 class.\r\n\r\n2. USELESS tutor. 2 hours class only taught for 10 minutes by the tutor. We paid for u. What\'s your attitude to teach us?\r\n\r\n3. Fee issues. We are taking classes ONLINE from home, are u kidding us to levy the \"Facilities & Resource Fee\" and \"Laboratory/Workshop\" fees. TARUC SRC indicates have communicated with Senior Management of TARUC. Then? Everything is just a show.', 'Information Technology', 2020, 78, 0, 0, 3, 0, 1, 1, NULL),
(262, '2021-08-27 14:45:08', 'Nicole', 'yeohml-wm20@student.tarc.edu.my', 'Good online learning environment. There are complete and sufficient notes provided by the lecturer. The lecturers and tutors are very friendly and their teaching methods are simple and easy to understand. Overall, this is a great learning experience for me.', 'Diploma in Information Technology', 2020, 78, 5, 5, 5, 5, 5, 1, NULL),
