(297, '2021-09-01 23:52:11', 'W.         D.', 'waidicktang@gmail.com', 'Been here for a few times before the pandemic, but I never have a chance to experience the campus life. So far all the classmates that I encountered are friendly and kind. I can see the school management team is putting up much effort to help their students during this tough times. For lectures and tutors, some are very nice and some are here just to read slides and goyang kaki. \r\n\r\nI think the place of our campus is quite strategic, as it is surrounded by all kinds of F&B shops and BMC mall is nearby. The vibes around here is quite good, just sometimes the assignment and task given are hectic and we will feel stressful.(Universiti Tak Ada Rehat)\r\n\r\n', 'Bachelor of Accounting', 2020, 1, 4, 4, 5, 4, 4, 1, '110.159.159.155'),
(298, '2021-09-02 09:48:38', 'My name is Dante', '197522@student.upm.edu.my', 'Some of the places did not have good wifi connection, it will be worse when raining. Additionally, some of the lecturers are very lazy and did not hear the opinions from students. Next, food is always the same, very boring. Management of the staff is very horrible, just know to stop the petition, did not know to have a look at the contents of the petition.\r\n\r\nHowever, the environment of UPM is very beautiful, many recreational activities can be done at UPM. Some of the places are suitable to use as photography locations.\r\n', 'Foreign Language Major in Mandarin Language', 2018, 48, 2, 5, 3, 2, 1, 1, '202.190.87.177'),
