(301, '2021-09-02 15:54:23', 'Zack Swon', '202029@student.upm.edu.my', 'College - Somehow WiFi connection in college quite weak and slow as when using data. Many mosquito as I almost every night gonna be biten but my roommate didn\'t.\r\n\r\nFood - most of the foods in food court are spicy and similar, not much various.\r\n\r\nTransportation - bus always overload in peak hour. If you don\'t mind, you can walk to college from campus.\r\n\r\nManagement - their attitudes are good and sometimes slow sometimes efficient.\r\n\r\nLecture - lecture hall cold and clean while lecturers got good and not good. ', 'Business Administration ', 2019, 48, 3, 4, 4, 2, 3, 1, '115.135.203.195'),
