(405, '2021-09-20 08:51:54', 'Yee Kai Ling', 'klingg1709@gmail.com', 'Most of the lecturers are former officers, they teach the students by sharing their working experiences. They are very professional. The facilities of the college are quite good. They have labs and lots of classroom at different places. The popularity of this college is design academy. Also have business academy and security academy. The security academy will be moving from PJ to cheras due to increasing of the numbers of students. The college donâ€™t have canteen but there have many restaurants around the college , so easy to find cuisine. However, the management is not good, need some improvement. The lazy staffs should be warned or fired owing to they made the students become messy and affect the students by holding off the works . So susah la ! Overall saito is a great platform for students to pursue their dreams such as becoming uniform officers . ğŸ‘ğŸ»', 'Diploma in law enforcement administration ', 2019, 101, 4, 5, 5, 5, 4, 1, '210.187.251.216'),
(406, '2021-09-20 08:52:24', 'Emily', 'yungwei1124@gmail.com', 'Lecturers are professional and friendly. Library in PJ campus is smaller than I expected but equipped with necessary reference books. There are two downsides at the campus - Elevator is very slow and difficult to find parking (can be overcome by taking the staircase and LRT respectively). Overall, I had a very pleasant experience at BAC. BAC prepared me well when I need to further my law studies in the UK. Would recommend my juniors to study there. ', 'UKT (Law)', 2018, 119, 3, 3, 5, 4, 4, 1, '175.141.102.39'),
