(421, '2021-09-20 12:26:40', 'Don\'t come ', 'jeffphoon88@gmail.com', 'The management really bad they won\'t help students to solve their problems, they just ask students solve it yourself. Only financial department best in UCSI. IIS always crash during course selection, but payment side won\'t crash. Don\'t drive to campus, walk if u can. Parking fees almost cost same as shopping mall and not enough parking space here.\r\n\r\nLecturers are good, 10 out of 2 will read the slides during lecture, others willing to help students.\r\n\r\nFacilities some are bad usually in block C broken chair & table. Library loud like pasar I don\'t know why.\r\n\r\nMany food around the campus, but quantity over quality. Only few are nice and cheap.\r\n\r\nLastly management really cares about their reputation, they force confession pages to shut down. Student representative won\'t voice out to help students, I think they also controlled by management.\r\n\r\nIf u are rich and want to find a good uni go taylor or others. Don\'t spend too much money on this uni and bad returns. ', 'Diploma in logistics management ', 2018, 46, 1, 1, 4, 5, 1, 1, '121.122.73.111'),
