(427, '2021-09-20 13:01:14', 'your friend', 'pylee0405@gmail.com', 'It cannot be denied that IMU is smaller compared to other university but I think overall the facilities and lecturer are very good. I\'m not sure for degree program but for Fis, the lecturer are responsible and willing to answer our question. They are friendly! Tbh there is little food choice in IMU, there is just a cafeteria and a mamak in the campus and not much restaurant or cafÃ© ard campus, unless u drive la. There is also a mentor-mentee system, u can ask ur mentor anythg if u hv any doubt or questions, and I think IMU\'s system is quite organized. IMU also has it own clinics and the hospital is still in progress. SO if you don\'t mind abt the food, I think IMU is a good choice for you to pursue your study here!', 'Foundation in Science', 2020, 36, 3, 4, 5, 3, 4, 1, '113.210.113.81'),
