(435, '2021-09-20 14:02:21', 'happy', 'jacky041294@gmail.com', 'Environment here is really great. If you really want to join this uni remember carefull to choose your grpmate!! If not your semester will be hard.If you driving a car,may be will be a bit difficult to find a parking, although there have a lot of parking.And the bus services,if you want to take bus to school in 8am class,you have to wake up very early because there will have many people and you will not able to get in the bus. Lastly,UTAR is still a recommended uni,hope you have a nice university life. Wish you all the best!', 'Bachelor of Marketing', 2019, 2, 5, 5, 4, 3, 4, 1, '42.190.209.120'),
