(450, '2021-09-20 17:32:25', 'i am ok', 'beck_kem@hotmail.com', 'Before I enter taylorâ€™s, everyone was like thatâ€™s a rich kid school. But to be honest, I never even saw one person drove like super expensive car to school or people that is straight up flexing their fatherâ€™s money.\r\nI think the transport system there is bad because there isnâ€™t any BRT or LRT station nearby (nearest one is like 15-20minutes away and without proper pedestrian pathway) and thereâ€™s only the bus by taylorâ€™s which comes every hour once but the fare is cheap. Other than that, there is not a lot of choice when comes to eating. \r\nSome lecturers are fine and good but some is just lazy so I have mixed feeling on this. Saw a lot of comments complaining about the management, so far I have not encountered any unpleasant experience with them, when I need to contact with them, they replied relatively quick.', 'Foundation in SC', 2020, 56, 4, 3, 4, 2, 4, 1, '113.210.55.153'),
