(463, '2021-09-20 22:47:59', 'KOK FU SHENG', 'kfssheng@gmail.com', 'I graduated here in 2018. My lecturers willing to go all out to help me to ensure I wouldn\'t left behind in classes/assignments and tutorials. I am grateful to be graduated here.\r\n\r\nHowever, the management, especially the student affairs are of no help. My item was stolen from library in 2017, nobody in student affairs would ever help me to look for my stolen bag or at least assist me to handle the situation, I have to handle it myself.\r\n\r\nStudent affairs I will rate 0. they are of no help.. so IUKL students, please take care of yourselves, the student affairs will never give assistance to you as they feel it is burdensome to them.\r\n\r\nThey too refuse to assist me when I am I need of looking for job. IUKL alumni also of no help whereas in Sunway University, they make the effort to help the student  to secure an interview at least.\r\n\r\nYou are on your own in this university.\r\n', 'Bachelor of Arts English for Professional Communication', 2018, 62, 4, 4, 5, 2, 0, 1, '60.50.58.253'),
(464, '2021-09-20 22:57:30', 'Nashe', 'nashlim2001@gmail.com', 'Great if you wish to go for an IT career. Facilities are superb(coz everyone contributed) with top-end techs and gadgets.\r\n\r\nFees wise is one of the major burdens coz it is really expensive compared with other unis, but the outcome of modules are actually quite great and students are actually easy to apply as a basic practical skill if follow lectures and tutorials.\r\n\r\nLecturers are mostly great but it is a fixed schedule so you can\'t be picky.', 'Data Analytics (Degree)', 2021, 41, 5, 4, 4, 3, 4, 1, '124.13.52.66'),
(465, '2021-09-20 23:09:14', 'Anonymous', 'momolau2001@gmail.com', 'The facilities are good compared to other university. However the environment is quite boring as there are not much malls or parks for student to play around.\r\n\r\nThe lecturers are overall kind and professional, just the assignments are the way too easy and outdated. I see other universities\' assignments are more difficult than ours.\r\n\r\nFor new comers you have to be very active in school activities else it would be quite boring.', 'Diploma in ICT specializing in Software Engineering', 2021, 41, 5, 4, 4, 3, 5, 1, '1.9.107.151'),
