(467, '2021-09-21 04:55:52', 'Sean Yeo', 'seanyeo0829@gmail.com', 'Affordable courses and the university is very conducive for learning. Lecturers are experienced and helpful. Campus is huge as compared to other local private universities and is located in near proximity to Kuala Lumpur City centre with convenient services transportation.', 'Cambridge A-Level Science', 2019, 78, 5, 5, 5, 4, 5, 1, '180.73.151.226'),
