(469, '2021-09-21 10:39:59', 'Lee Sean', 'www.vern1997@gmail.com', 'Lift very slow, so many people using one small lift, 2 of the lift always in idle status, cant move, the food not nice, but lecturers very very very good. no parking, parking expensive somore, cant apply for monthly parking summore', 'Alevels Law n CLP', 2014, 119, 2, 3, 4, 1, 4, 1, '121.123.72.226'),
(470, '2021-09-21 14:06:53', 'Jeffchua', 'jeffchua213@gmail.com', 'blood sucking uni, no discount during MCO and still need to pay facility and lab fees, activity fees even though we are not allowed to go back to campus, when ask related question about the fees, they only know how to kick the ball, from department to department, somemore give lousy reason like \" we are expecting students to continue their lab after MCO lifted, come on lah, face the truth, by the time MCO lift some already graduated. Also some of the lec very loust, no free thinker allowed , you can only stick with their lecture notes, so dont act smart, be dumb and copy answer from notes.', 'Food science', 2021, 46, 2, 2, 3, 4, 1, 1, '115.164.223.94'),
(471, '2021-09-21 14:24:26', 'Cocoo', 'leezaixii@gmail.com', 'Environment is really nice,quiet, not like a city, u can fishing there also. No have more entertainment like shopping mall but got ktv, cinema and mamak. If you don\'t have car, you can use bicycle, ebike or school bus go to school also. Not recommend walking, cuz campus is really big and have many blocks.\r\nMany hostels near campus and rental is cheap, it  takes 6,7min walk from your hostel to only campus gate and take another 8,10min walk to your blocks. Lecturers are nice and explain the subject clearly but not all like that, hope u meet the nice one.\r\nManagement will not response to your request or question as fast,takes few days but during MCO they reply fast by email in the same day.\r\nFood is okay,we have many canteens in campus since it\'s big. Block C,H,K got at least one each.\r\nFacilities seems okay, u can use the empty classroom if there is no class using,library has many seat for student but better come early in exam week.\r\nLastly, if you are using bicycle as transportation, u will have a strong healthy body, I have ride bicycle almost two years to school and less 5-8kg in these two years.\r\nHope u enjoy your school life, don\'t give yourselves too much study stress.', 'Entrepreneurship', 2018, 2, 4, 5, 3, 4, 3, 1, '180.73.39.92'),
(472, '2021-09-21 15:03:03', 'Anonymous', 'lky19.99@gmail.com', 'FIS is quite easy , sleep also can get 4.0 Almost like honeymoon year. FIS Lecturers are friendly and they teach quite well, compared to MBBS . If MBBS , only a few lecturers are really teaching, others are just loafers. Sometimes, self learning is more efficient. Overall still okay, i will rate 7/10 for MBBS. Definitely not satisfied with the management, they prioritize MONEY MORE, yet not efficiency. DONT STAY HOSTEL!!! Choices of food in campus is limited, better to have own transportation. ', 'FIS,MBBS', 2030, 64, 4, 3, 2, 1, 1, 1, '210.195.80.120'),
