(490, '2021-09-22 04:08:54', 'Bald SE girl', 'wenhuiiyang@gmail.com', 'Tuition Fees not the same as stated in the website or brochure. After the pandemic happen they still having the facilities fee without any thing list out in the student bill. Some lecturers are good but most of them just read slides. Management is the worst if you apply loan with them. Every trimester need to submit the same document. Slow like snail. Exam hard af. 45 minutes 101 mcq question plus submission time. Final Assessment only 20-30% have taught in lecture class. Others need to be learn by yourself or google. Sometime google also didnâ€™t have so good luck yall ', 'Bachelor of Science(Honours) Software Engineering ', 2019, 1, 3, 3, 2, 4, 1, 1, '124.13.198.117'),
