(492, '2021-09-22 10:16:23', 'Golden', 'kamkahhoe1216@gmail.com', 'lecture some are good and some are soso but overall is oklah. Cost also in acceptable and inexpensive.TarUC Kl Campus environment is nice and uni have alot of lengluii and lengzaii!!The transportation is convenient. Although now is online learning environment but not bad for me however the online assessment is kinda difficult and kbat.', 'diploma in Hotel Management ', 2020, 78, 4, 4, 4, 4, 3, 1, '115.164.218.133'),
