(494, '2021-09-22 12:58:14', 'Ryan the Lion', 'leahfung99@hotmail.com', 'Kampar Campus. Good and relaxing environment unlike those in the city. Food is not as good as Penang but acceptable la (expensive sia). Would be the best uni life where you will be independent and spend most of your time with friends. As...there\'s no shopping malls or fancy restaurants but mamak, spades and cinema (closed down liao oh). If your friends has car, can even travel to Ipoh or other places during weekends or sem break. Definitely no regrets here for my uni life and wish I could do it again.\r\n\r\nManagement wise, so so only lo. Don\'t expect so much. Facility ok la. Block C atm always let rich students withdraw until empty. Parking beh tahan lo, either you are early and wait kao kao or you are late and round for half an hour. Oh ya, good luck in bidding timetable ya.\r\n\r\nLecturer, assignment and teammates leh. See your luck d. You will have good lecturer and responsible teammates if you are lucky. Or you will be living in hell.\r\n\r\nOverall ok la. Really suffered (academic) and enjoyed (life) in this uni (Kampar). If you are looking for cheap uni, challenging education, independent life, go for it. Honestly spending time and travel with friends crazily is really a precious thing you could get here. Only if there\'s no MCO or Covid. Byeee, off to look back at my memorable pictures!\r\n\r\nINCREASE OR DECREASE? CREASEEEEEEE', 'Financial Economics', 2021, 2, 4, 5, 4, 3, 3, 1, '202.190.85.129'),
(495, '2021-09-22 14:14:17', 'ChinoRabbit_69', 'www.zhengliang@gmail.com', 'Environment is perfect, is good place to relax and study. The place is big, those buildings are around of the big lake. Be careful of the wild animals(just don\'t stay to close). The cafeteria\'s food price is cheaper than outside foods.\r\n\r\nYou can choose driving, ebike, school bus or cycling to the school. If you choose driving, you must need to buy car sticker to allow enter the campus(for semester), if not you can drive to outside east gate to take parking, follow the traffic road and avoid a \"free ticket\", and keep the eyes out for the ebike. \r\n\r\nThe hostel you need to find by you own, many of my friends are rent in Westlake Danish house, rental is around RM150(suggest). The thing is ok, the more information can ask the Danish management. I am current rent in Westlake Villas small single room, price is RM350. Good facilities, \"Much price have good things\".\r\n\r\nThere are haven\'t many entertainment like big shopping mall, mamak, cinema and kopitiam. Don\'t worry about the food anyway. If you have car, please drive smart, the thing worse than your imagine.\r\n\r\nEducation is cheap than other collage/uni, but final exam is hard(honestly, thing is never ez in your life.) If you fear about this, you can extands the programme progress and don\'t take to much of courses in each semester\r\n\r\nAbout IB, thing is force IT and business. If you interest the business and IT(coding), is good to you. No much harder than other IT courses. But I suggest my little friends that study your likely course, build your own road. If not, this course is too hard for you, so think carefully about your future.', 'Business Information System', 2019, 2, 4, 5, 3, 4, 4, 1, '27.125.249.15'),
